OL,3,CColin Smyth MSP understood to be
OL,4,Cfacing charges over camera in Holyrood
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth has
OL,8,Fbeen effectively barred from the
OL,9,FScottish parliament amid an ongoing
OL,10,Fpolice investigation.
OL,12,FITV Border last week revealed that he
OL,13,Fhad been suspended by Labour. He has
OL,14,Fbeen charged by Police Scotland and is
OL,15,Fexpected to appear in court at a later
OL,16,Fdate.
OL,18,FThe Daily Record reported on Thursday
OL,19,Fthat Mr Smyth has been charged with
OL,20,Fplacing a camera in a toilet in the
OL,21,FScottish parliament building.
