OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FLast week, detectives confirmed that
OL,8,Fhe had been charged with possession of
OL,9,Findecent images.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, a Police Scotland
OL,12,Fspokesperson said: "On Tuesday, 5
OL,13,FAugust, 2025, officers executed a
OL,14,Fwarrant at a property in Dumfries and
OL,15,Fa 52-year-old man was arrested and
OL,16,Fcharged as part of an ongoing
OL,17,Finvestigation. He is due to appear at
OL,18,FDumfries Sheriff Court at a later
OL,19,Fdate."
