OL,7,FSome members of the parliament were
OL,8,Fthen made aware by their
OL,9,Frepresentative on the cross-party
OL,10,Fgroup that "a significant and damaging
OL,11,Fstory is likely to break regarding a
OL,12,Fmatter at Holyrood, at some point this
OL,13,Fevening".
OL,15,FIn an email to MSPs, the parliament's
OL,16,Fchief executive David McGill said the
OL,17,Fdecision had been taken because of the
OL,18,F"serious criminal charges" brought
OL,19,Fagainst Mr Smyth.
