OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FHe added: "We recognise the nature of
OL,8,Fthe criminal charges and the ongoing
OL,9,Finvestigation may be upsetting for
OL,10,Fcolleagues and cause distress. We
OL,11,Fwould therefore like to remind
OL,12,Feveryone who works at Holyrood or in
OL,13,Fconstituency offices of the
OL,14,Fconfidential support services that are
OL,15,Favailable."
OL,17,FLast week, Mr Smyth said the "events
OL,18,Fhave come as a shock and this is a
OL,19,Fdeeply stressful time" and promised to
OL,20,Fcooperate with the police
OL,21,Finvestigation.
